1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,740
=Episode 20=

3
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:05,879
Your Majesty.

4
00:01:05,879 --> 00:01:06,519
Zhaohua.

5
00:01:07,879 --> 00:01:09,519
Greetings, Your Majesty.

6
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:10,480
Zhaohua.

7
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:12,760
Why are you being so distant?

8
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:14,599
Are you still angry with me?

9
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:16,000
I wouldn't dare.

10
00:01:17,599 --> 00:01:19,319
I am Your Majesty's consort.

11
00:01:19,319 --> 00:01:21,040
My life is yours.

12
00:01:21,519 --> 00:01:23,079
However you wish to dispose of me,

13
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:25,079
I have no right to complain.

14
00:01:26,719 --> 00:01:27,640
So it seems

15
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,280
you're still angry with me.

16
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,280
I admit

17
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:35,799
there was a time

18
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:37,120
after you gave birth,

19
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,879
I considered handing you over
to Jiang Yukui.

20
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,280
But back then,

21
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:45,079
my feelings for you

22
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,640
were all because of the child
you carried.

23
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,159
But when I held

24
00:01:59,439 --> 00:02:00,599
this child,

25
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,599
our child,

26
00:02:03,359 --> 00:02:04,200
and remembered

27
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,319
all the moments between us,

28
00:02:06,879 --> 00:02:07,840
I realized

29
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:09,800
I was about to lose you,

30
00:02:10,599 --> 00:02:12,240
and it broke my heart.

31
00:02:13,599 --> 00:02:14,680
Zhaohua, hold him.

32
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,319
To me,

33
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,759
you have become indispensable.

34
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,400
This realm,

35
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,360
without you,

36
00:02:30,919 --> 00:02:32,240
would lose its light.

37
00:02:34,039 --> 00:02:35,039
My whole life,

38
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,280
I want to spend it

39
00:02:40,199 --> 00:02:41,400
with you always.

40
00:02:46,159 --> 00:02:46,919
Actually,

41
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,199
I could have told you

42
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,159
that everything I said to Jiang Yukui

43
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,319
was a lie.

44
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,840
But I chose to be honest with you.

45
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,439
Do you know why?

46
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:00,919
Why?

47
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,360
Because I don't

48
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,639
want to lie to you anymore.

49
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,240
I want to hold your hand

50
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,439
and grow old with you

51
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:23,080
together.

52
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,639
If you still can't forgive me,

53
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,000
then let's go
to the Palace of Punishment.

54
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:30,479
I'll

55
00:03:31,319 --> 00:03:32,400
let you torture me.

56
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:33,960
No.

57
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:38,000
How could I bear to hurt you?

58
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,560
Your Majesty.

59
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:46,280
If you truly want to make me happy,

60
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:48,000
why not do something

61
00:03:48,879 --> 00:03:50,639
I actually enjoy?

62
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:52,000
Fine.

63
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:53,400
I'll do as you wish.

64
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:55,719
Whatever you want, I'll do it all.

65
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,599
Touch him.

66
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,360
He looks just like you.

67
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:14,120
You just said

68
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,759
you'd do whatever I want.

69
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,279
So let's

70
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:19,959
play a game.

71
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:21,240
Alright.

72
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:25,399
All of you, hide yourselves well.

73
00:04:26,079 --> 00:04:27,480
After one incense stick's time,

74
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:30,120
if anyone is still alive,

75
00:04:30,759 --> 00:04:32,000
they will receive

76
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,079
ten thousand taels of gold.

77
00:04:34,079 --> 00:04:35,800
Whether you live or die

78
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:39,680
is up to your own fate.

79
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:42,639
Your Majesty.

80
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,759
If you win today,

81
00:04:44,759 --> 00:04:46,199
I'll forgive you.

82
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,600
But if you lose,

83
00:04:50,519 --> 00:04:52,279
there will be a penalty.

84
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:54,959
What penalty?

85
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,439
You'll be forbidden from seeing

86
00:04:57,439 --> 00:04:59,720
me and our child for a month.

87
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:02,439
Then I suppose

88
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,399
I must win.

89
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:16,319
My dear.

90
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,439
Where are they?

91
00:05:17,639 --> 00:05:18,120
There.

92
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,639
Found you!

93
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,120
My dear.

94
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,600
I leave him to you.

95
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,639
Thank you, Your Majesty.

96
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:56,639
Hyah!

97
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,319
Hyah!

98
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:06,079
Hyah!

99
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:08,399
Hyah!

100
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:28,560
Come.

101
00:06:29,519 --> 00:06:30,240
It's time to eat.

102
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,879
Why do you

103
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:37,439
suddenly want to drink?

104
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,360
I was thinking

105
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,439
we've known each other so long,

106
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,720
yet I've never shared a proper drink

107
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:50,240
or a real conversation with you.

108
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:54,079
And tonight's moonlight is perfect.

109
00:06:54,959 --> 00:06:56,560
So I thought I'd seize the moment

110
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,199
and have a drink with you.

111
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,800
You won't join me?

112
00:07:03,279 --> 00:07:05,240
Through fire and water, I'd follow you.

113
00:07:05,439 --> 00:07:06,639
A few drinks are nothing.

114
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,439
Here.

115
00:07:11,879 --> 00:07:13,959
But drinking alone is dull.

116
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:15,079
How about

117
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,800
we play a drinking game?

118
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:18,319
Do you want to recite poetry

119
00:07:18,319 --> 00:07:19,480
or compose couplets?

120
00:07:21,199 --> 00:07:21,839
Neither.

121
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:24,560
In my Zhao Tribe,

122
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,680
there's a different game.

123
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,120
For every cup you drink,

124
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:29,160
you may ask one question,

125
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,879
and the other must answer truthfully.

126
00:07:33,079 --> 00:07:33,560
Alright.

127
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,439
I'll go first.

128
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:44,040
Back then, you said you wanted me
to be your needle.

129
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,399
Was that your true intention?

130
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,040
No.

131
00:07:51,959 --> 00:07:53,160
I only meant

132
00:07:53,879 --> 00:07:55,279
for you to be my arrow

133
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,560
to wound Rong Xiu.

134
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,839
If you ever became a threat,

135
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,600
I could discard you at any time.

136
00:08:02,959 --> 00:08:03,680
But...

137
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,079
Wait.

138
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,160
I haven't asked yet.

139
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,319
My turn.

140
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:20,839
When you first met me,

141
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:22,920
what did you think?

142
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:29,879
Arrogant,

143
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:31,399
self-righteous.

144
00:08:31,959 --> 00:08:33,759
Thinking you could use me

145
00:08:34,879 --> 00:08:36,559
and putting me to the test.

146
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,159
But you didn't know.

147
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,759
You were my prey all along.

148
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,159
I want to keep asking.

149
00:08:54,919 --> 00:08:55,919
I want to know

150
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,679
what your childhood was like.

151
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,879
For that, you'll have to drink
three cups.

152
00:09:06,639 --> 00:09:08,240
It's a long story.

153
00:09:14,260 --> 00:09:17,460
♪The moon sinks in the west.
The cold lamp burns low♪

154
00:09:17,740 --> 00:09:20,620
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

155
00:09:21,180 --> 00:09:24,660
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

156
00:09:27,900 --> 00:09:31,300
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard,
yet love and hate entwine♪

157
00:09:31,460 --> 00:09:34,820
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

158
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:38,780
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

159
00:09:39,980 --> 00:09:43,140
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

160
00:09:43,140 --> 00:09:46,700
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

161
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:49,020
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

162
00:09:49,020 --> 00:09:53,220
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

163
00:09:53,660 --> 00:09:56,820
♪The green lamp sheds no light
upon one who entered the path♪

164
00:09:57,180 --> 00:10:00,380
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

165
00:10:00,620 --> 00:10:04,100
♪In dreams, it's you.
Beyond dreams, no one♪

166
00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:07,100
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

167
00:10:07,100 --> 00:10:10,380
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

168
00:10:10,380 --> 00:10:13,900
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

169
00:10:14,220 --> 00:10:17,300
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

170
00:10:17,300 --> 00:10:20,700
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪

171
00:10:32,039 --> 00:10:32,840
Feng Ye.

172
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:35,120
Wait for me.

173
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:38,279
Soon, we'll leave together.

174
00:11:13,759 --> 00:11:15,080
Your Majesty.

175
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,200
Wait for me.

176
00:11:20,159 --> 00:11:21,879
You must be wondering

177
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:24,759
why I summoned you here today.

178
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:28,919
Your Majesty is wise and mighty,

179
00:11:28,919 --> 00:11:30,399
diligent in governance,

180
00:11:30,799 --> 00:11:33,879
which is why we enjoy this era
of peace and prosperity.

181
00:11:34,279 --> 00:11:35,720
Yet within the palace,

182
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:37,960
there is a treacherous consort, Rong,

183
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:40,200
who abuses your favor

184
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,679
and brings chaos to the harem.

185
00:11:42,159 --> 00:11:43,639
If this continues,

186
00:11:43,799 --> 00:11:46,200
it may tarnish Your Majesty's virtue.

187
00:11:47,759 --> 00:11:49,519
I beg Your Majesty

188
00:11:49,519 --> 00:11:51,360
to strip her of her title

189
00:11:51,879 --> 00:11:53,799
and sentence her to death.

190
00:11:54,559 --> 00:11:56,720
If Your Majesty insists
on tolerating her,

191
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:59,200
I will have no choice
but to retire and return home.

192
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,200
I speak with tears.

193
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:06,080
How dare you

194
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:08,200
read His Majesty's memorials!

195
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,519
Don't you know

196
00:12:09,519 --> 00:12:10,840
a consort cannot interfere
in state affairs?

197
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:13,399
I told Zhaohua to read them.

198
00:12:14,799 --> 00:12:15,200
This...

199
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:17,639
I beg

200
00:12:17,799 --> 00:12:19,919
Your Majesty to see the truth!

201
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,159
Consort Rong

202
00:12:22,159 --> 00:12:23,559
has conspired with her family

203
00:12:23,559 --> 00:12:24,799
and thrown the court into chaos.

204
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,720
Within the palace,

205
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:28,000
she has used her charms to mislead you,

206
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:31,279
destroying a century of our Kun legacy.

207
00:12:31,279 --> 00:12:32,639
Such a treacherous consort.

208
00:12:33,039 --> 00:12:34,240
She cannot remain!

209
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:35,039
- Outrageous!
- Your Majesty.

210
00:12:37,879 --> 00:12:39,799
Zhaohua's brother rendered
great service to the throne.

211
00:12:39,799 --> 00:12:40,919
Now Zhaohua

212
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:42,720
has borne me a son.

213
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,720
She is no treacherous consort.

214
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:46,159
She is my blessing,

215
00:12:46,159 --> 00:12:47,799
the blessing of all Kun!

216
00:12:47,799 --> 00:12:49,320
Your Majesty.

217
00:12:50,919 --> 00:12:52,120
And you...

218
00:12:52,679 --> 00:12:54,120
How dare you!

219
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,399
Your Majesty, please calm down.

220
00:12:56,399 --> 00:12:58,639
You're accusing me
in such a roundabout way,

221
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:00,120
saying

222
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:01,799
that I cannot protect Kun

223
00:13:01,799 --> 00:13:03,440
and need a woman to take the blame
for my failures.

224
00:13:03,879 --> 00:13:04,799
You old fool.

225
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:06,440
Since you're old

226
00:13:07,279 --> 00:13:09,039
and still can't keep your mouth shut,

227
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:10,960
I'll teach you a lesson.

228
00:13:11,559 --> 00:13:12,120
Guards!

229
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:20,200
You tyrant.

230
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:22,919
You've been

231
00:13:22,919 --> 00:13:25,720
bewitched by this treacherous consort.
You can't tell right from wrong.

232
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:26,919
You cruel tyrant.

233
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:27,639
You...

234
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:31,799
You will lose the people's trust!

235
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,320
The state is well-governed,

236
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,559
and the realm is at peace.

237
00:13:34,879 --> 00:13:37,120
The people adore His Majesty.

238
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:38,840
How could he have lost their trust?

239
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,360
In my view,

240
00:13:40,759 --> 00:13:43,279
what His Majesty has lost
is your heart, Grand Tutor.

241
00:13:43,679 --> 00:13:45,360
Now that His Majesty rules directly,

242
00:13:45,759 --> 00:13:48,240
you have lost your grip on him.

243
00:13:48,639 --> 00:13:50,080
That is why you're dissatisfied.

244
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:52,159
Daring to bully His Majesty?

245
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,320
Today,

246
00:13:54,759 --> 00:13:56,039
I'll show you

247
00:13:56,279 --> 00:13:57,600
what I'm capable of.

248
00:14:06,919 --> 00:14:09,200
Feng Ye is toying with me.

249
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:11,399
He promised to help me
with my great cause,

250
00:14:11,639 --> 00:14:13,639
but now he's backed out
at the last moment.

251
00:14:15,159 --> 00:14:16,320
How outrageous!

252
00:14:16,639 --> 00:14:17,159
Marquis.

253
00:14:17,279 --> 00:14:18,320
What should we do then?

254
00:14:18,679 --> 00:14:19,840
What to do?

255
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,240
What else can we do?

256
00:14:21,639 --> 00:14:22,559
We have to go back.

257
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:23,480
Unless we want

258
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,519
His Majesty to find us here.

259
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:27,519
You hold military power, Marquis.

260
00:14:27,919 --> 00:14:29,559
If you wanted the realm,

261
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:31,120
why rely on others?

262
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,039
Holy Maiden.

263
00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:34,720
Did His Lordship send you?

264
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,679
Who sent me doesn't matter.

265
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:38,200
What matters

266
00:14:38,519 --> 00:14:40,240
is that I can help you.

267
00:14:41,759 --> 00:14:43,399
If even Feng Ye couldn't do it,

268
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,240
what makes you think you can?

269
00:14:48,399 --> 00:14:49,000
Marquis.

270
00:14:51,060 --> 00:14:52,380
(Decree)

271
00:14:55,500 --> 00:14:59,940
(Decree)

272
